relation: Twinkling lights to adorn your Frostfell tree!
pageTitle: Feelin' Gifty in Freeport! :: Quests :: EverQuest II :: ZAM
textBeforeTable: The Gigglegibber goblin was very happy with my assistance, and has granted me the ability to adorn the Frostfell tree that Gh'lad Tydingz rewarded me with. I delivered all the gifts to the right citizens! I spoke to G'shugahplum. Complete: Return to G'shugahplum. Start: Stage 4Whether the gifts went to the person that G'shugahplum had intended, I do not know. I should now return to G'shugahplum. I have delivered all of the gifts that were given to me. I gave a gift to Klaessa L'tek. Complete: Deliver a gift to Klaessa L'tek. Start: I gave a gift to Gemellus Sperasius. Complete: Deliver a gift to Gemellus Sperasius. Start: I gave a gift to Kamaria Cheefar. Complete: Deliver a gift to Kamaria Cheefar. Start: I gave a gift to Thabit Kalila. Complete: Deliver a gift to Thabit Kalila. Start: I gave a gift to Gowan Macgillivray. Complete: Deliver a gift to Gowan Macgillivray.
